title: Nations Pledge to Protect Animal, Plant Diversity
description: Nearly 200 countries reached the nonbinding deal, which targets conserving at least 30% of land and water areas by 2030.

title: Five Killed at Canada Condo Shooting in 'Horrendous Scene'
description: Police in Vaughan, Ontario, didn’t immediately identify the suspected shooter or a possible motive.

title: Thai Navy Searches for 31 Sailors After Storm Sinks Warship
description: The HTMS Sukhothai was carrying a crew of 106 sailors before it sank in the Gulf of Thailand.

title: Russia and China to Hold Joint Naval Drills
description: The drills highlight the close partnership between the two nations as the Kremlin seeks to bolster support among partners to offset western isolation for its war in Ukraine.

title: China Records First Deaths After Easing Covid-19 Policy, With Many More Likely
description: Lack of data and confusion over new rules mean the true scale of wave engulfing nation remains a mystery.

title: European Energy Ministers Push for Natural-Gas Price Cap
description: Russia’s invasion of Ukraine has sent prices soaring, but an agreement to limit costs has eluded the officials, who are meeting for the second time in one week.

title: South African President Ramaphosa Is Re-Elected as Party Leader
description: Cyril Ramaphosa shrugged off a parliamentary investigation that found he may have violated the country’s constitution, as well as a forceful challenge by allies of his disgraced predecessor.

title: Drones Strike Ukraine as Kyiv Scrambles to Restore Power and Heating
description: Russia launched a fresh wave of drone attacks as Ukraine struggled to repair energy infrastructure damaged by recent missile attacks that have left millions without power.

title: Italy Found a Fix for Its Gas Crisis, but Locals Are Resisting
description: A town in Tuscany is fighting against an LNG terminal that Italy says is urgently needed as part of Europe’s efforts to replace Russian energy.
